FIGURE 2.

Empis
(
Sphenempis
) 
bicoloriventris


sp. nov.

, paratype male from Okinawa-jima. 
A,
head, lateral aspect; 
B,
antenna; 
C,
labium, lateral aspect; 
D,
ditto, ventral aspect; 
E,
labellum, lateral aspect; 
F,
apex of labrum, anterior aspect; 
G,
maxillary palpus. Scale bars = 0.5 mm (A, C. D), 0.2 mm (B, G), 0.1 mm (E, F).
